Folder symbols
-=-=-=-=-=-=-=
TOOLS_DIR - store/tools
STORE_DIR - store
ROOT_DIR - store folder. Obsoleted

TASKS_DIR - new. for tasks.work

Library names
-=-=-=-=-=-=-
niver - fund, data, gui. Not sure about this name.
tools - store functionality.


Folder structure
-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=
page.php - the html page displayed. will be replaced in the integration with wordpress by shortcode.
admin-post.php handles operations.
admin.php - all the functional code. including wont display noting.
Object.php - code handling a class.


inputs
-=-=-=

New row - field name will be just the field name. Will be handled by save_new or save_new_custom.
Existing row - field name will be <field>_<row_number>. Will be handled by update_entity.